title: Lost 80s LPs Two People - The Collection
description:
I will start posting some real rare 80s LPs that are lost in time and never got released as a digital format. Statring with Two People. They were a Brit band of the mid-80s, who released a full album [Heaven] and a handful of singles. But the music they made was just fantastic. so here you are. This is The Shirt, Rescue Me, Mouth of An Angel, Heaven, Let&#039;s Raise Murder and Back Into The Room Of Blue are the standout tunes. After the video of Rescue Me was posted on Youtube, their music has attracted many new listeners and brought back memories for those who knew them. This for sure it&#039;s an amazing piece of new romantic music.
